{"tid":273472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以忘記一個人","createTime":"2017-06-06T14:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T03:22:03.000Z","uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3786e0f6732a7a4d493a0f1a0d0188e375d9e34","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"同佢識左幾個月 一直都好好傾 直至上個禮拜同佢表左白 然後佢就好快收左我皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問翻佢咩原因拒絕我都無答我<br />\n而家就算做乜都諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee8cdffeea83cc4cd13dedd9f87068ef925a4fa","tid":273472,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"失憶"},{"pid":"814700da3ebfd0f1df8b9277b9cce461f3ae505a","tid":273472,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"毒撚總係以為好傾=得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻鳩黎既"},{"pid":"9df65558a08cd57b6b10bce321e64078e6510763","tid":273472,"uid":97863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"（認真）識下一個，你依加掛著佢係因為冇得揀先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d813693173151ea3a539629395356c0080be65","tid":273472,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚總係以為好傾=得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻鳩黎既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗返起都覺得自己on9"},{"pid":"c0617e7b9340f85c5613a10f82ef81b8713716ed","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚總係以為好傾=得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻鳩黎既</blockquote><br />\n其實我知佢對我無feel 因爲平時我講野哄佢佢都好少理 只係我一廂情願 諗住同佢表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41330a468f95dac3796ff59828416ec36327af8b","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>（認真）識下一個，你依加掛著佢係因為冇得揀先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係唔係話識就識 加上岩岩完左sem..."},{"pid":"64689257cc397a23b36b08b953e865af8036b53a","tid":273472,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"我也曾像這樣 青春大概相似<br />\n總有段情陷入這種困局"},{"pid":"d942370b9fa0518e766a236632ff4e6e378689b9","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我也曾像這樣 青春大概相似<br />\n總有段情陷入這種困局</blockquote><br />\n好難走出呢個困局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上一無野做就諗起佢"},{"pid":"49a28d63db211dacf16c968ae343362542ad63e4","tid":273472,"uid":6909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"搵過第二個傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967a9908c70e966ff3e001b8452f2b6be9a6fc4a","tid":273472,"uid":117923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵過第二個傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 搵第二個人傾 或者做其他野轉移視線"},{"pid":"8ec4ed890de541d2c2bb898ba924a4653514650d","tid":273472,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>毒撚總係以為好傾=得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻鳩黎既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗返起都覺得自己on9</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b542366d2ef425c904ba604bf29c7c0476b3668c","tid":273472,"uid":121360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我也曾像這樣 青春大概相似<br />\n總有段情陷入這種困局</blockquote><br />\n好難走出呢個困局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上一無野做就諗起佢</blockquote><br />\n你都識講 無野做就會諗起<br />\n咁搵多啲野做，等自己忙啲 過得充實啲就唔得閒諗咁多"},{"pid":"169ea692e910e2fbc6e67ff8d62d8a192c76873b","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"恰埋眼都諗起佢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb39f06d555ddeb1c8d625b2f419f195af5cb8e","tid":273472,"uid":111920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"佢唔中意你！算把啦<br />\n除非你吸引到佢 不過知道你咁中意佢 都唔會點care你"},{"pid":"c16cc94df5004e8163a1d3ac692ac9e5acf2d303","tid":273472,"uid":106978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T18:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恰埋眼都諗起佢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪繼續諗囉，諗諗下就發現有啲人只係適合用黎ff，由始至終冇適合過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ef5382df6de0c80050b31b67fb0f96a4e1b95a","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>恰埋眼都諗起佢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪繼續諗囉，諗諗下就發現有啲人只係適合用黎ff，由始至終冇適合過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b124888b17a0812e06ea4b011d6fb15e45b700","tid":273472,"uid":1247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"忘記不了 只好改變心態<br />\n好好的放在回憶裡 不刻意去思索<br />\n把對話封存 合照刪掉 一切有關她的都隱藏<br />\n到有另一人出現的時候 <br />\n自自然然 你就能放下"},{"pid":"64e3cfccc9bc6e3ebb0d83bf538f5ae583db66db","tid":273472,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"_ _ _ 謝天華"},{"pid":"b5909c758519e7f1e239ef4a1db99cb8606f09b5","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忘記不了 只好改變心態<br />\n好好的放在回憶裡 不刻意去思索<br />\n把對話封存 合照刪掉 一切有關她的都隱藏<br />\n到有另一人出現的時候 <br />\n自自然然 你就能放下</blockquote><br />\n岩既我都明 我已經del晒所有野 又封存埋 但係呢段時間真係好難捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d131aa82df9d4b09856dad8c1456667d75294b06","tid":273472,"uid":51750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>_ _ _ 謝天華</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦我又未去到呢個地步既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}